<darkcolour>A6416E</darkcolour><section><title>Requests and suggestions with &lt;I&gt;can&lt;/I&gt;</title><sectiontitle>Use &lt;I&gt;Can you&lt;/I&gt; + verb to make requests.</sectiontitle><titlesound>ELEMGRAM_3_3_1.mp3</titlesound><text1>take a message</text1><sound1>ELEMGRAM_3_3_2.mp3</sound1><text1a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;Can you&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; take a message?</text1a><text2>come to the shop this week</text2><sound2>ELEMGRAM_3_3_3.mp3</sound2><text2a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;Can you&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; come to the shop this week?</text2a><titlesound2>ELEMGRAM_3_3_4.mp3</titlesound2><sectiontitle2>Use &lt;I&gt;Why don't we&lt;/I&gt; + verb? or &lt;I&gt;How about&lt;/I&gt; + noun? to make suggestions.</sectiontitle2><text3>have dinner this evening</text3><sound3>ELEMGRAM_3_3_5.mp3</sound3><text3a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;Why don't we&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; have dinner this evening?</text3a><text4>lunch on Friday</text4><sound4>ELEMGRAM_3_3_6.mp3</sound4><text4a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;How about&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; lunch on Friday?</text4a></section><section><title>Requests and suggestions with &lt;I&gt;can&lt;/I&gt;</title><sectiontitle>We also use &lt;I&gt;Let's&lt;/I&gt; + verb to make a suggestion.</sectiontitle><titlesound>ELEMGRAM_3_3_7.mp3</titlesound><text1>see a film this evening</text1><sound1>ELEMGRAM_3_3_8.mp3</sound1><text1a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;Let's&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; see a film this evening.</text1a><text2>meet outside the cinema</text2><sound2>ELEMGRAM_3_3_9.mp3</sound2><text2a>&lt;B&gt;&lt;Font color='#A6416E'&gt;Let's&lt;/Font&gt;&lt;/B&gt; meet outside the cinema at eight o'clock.</text2a><titlesound2>%undefined</titlesound2><sectiontitle2>%undefined</sectiontitle2><text3>%undefined</text3><sound3>%undefined</sound3><text3a>%undefined</text3a><text4>%undefined</text4><sound4>%undefined</sound4><text4a>%undefined</text4a></section></grammar>